question: Who becomes world's highest paid model in 2017?
explanation: American model Kendall Jenner beat Gisele Bundchen to become the world's highest-earning model in 2017, as per Forbes Report. The 22-year-old model's earnings have been estimated to be $22 million (142crores). Gisele, who has been the highest-paid model since 2002, was ranked second in the list this year, with earnings of $17.5 million (113 crores).
